it and spices. It is typically served with meats, such as steak, burgers, pork ribs or chicken.","If using wooden skewers, pre-soak them in water to make sure they do not catch alight.","You can prepare the monkey gland sauce up to <b>1 week<b> ahead and keep it in the fridge in a jar."],"basicInfo":["easy","25m","2h","4 portions"]}